Package: comorbidPRS
Title: Assessing the shared predisposition between Phenotypes using Polygenic Scores (PGS, or PRS/GRS for binary outcomes)
Version: 0.3.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Vincent", "Pascat", , "vincent.pascat@univ-lille.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6227-8812"))
Description: Using Polygenic Scores (PGS, or PRS/GRS for binary outcomes), 
    this package allows to investigate shared predisposition between different 
    Conditions, and do fast analysis on different Phenotypes, export interesting
    views of the PGS distribution using ggplot2 graphs. 
